zones, representing lithospheric sutures of the Amazonian and São
Francisco Cratons, Tocantins Province and Parnaíba Block. In
addition, coincident residual gravity, residual magnetic, and
pseudo-gravity lows indicate two complex systems of Eopaleozoic rifts
